twitter-backup

Main Features:
- backup of all my tweets + all related tweets
- storage in database + human readable file(s)
- ability to search tweets

Detailed Backup Features:
- all my tweets

Implementation:
- Node.js
- CouchDB

Configuration:
- edit config-default.json or override with config.json

